OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FThe First Minister says she is very
OL,8,Fcomfortable with her decision to stay
OL,9,Faway from a defence investment
OL,10,Fannouncement.
OL,12,FMichelle O'Neill spoke to UTV ahead of
OL,13,FSinn Fein's Ard Fheis at the weekend.
OL,15,FDefence minister Luke Pollard visited
OL,16,FBelfast on Wednesday with Northern
OL,17,FIreland Office minister Matthew
OL,18,FPatrick to meet representatives from
OL,19,Flocal industry and research, to launch
OL,20,Fthe Northern Ireland Defence Growth
OL,21,FDeal.
OL,26,@uD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
