FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FOfficials said the deal ` part of the
OL,8,FUK Government's Defence Industrial
OL,9,FStrategy, will create a targeted
OL,10,Fprogramme to help small and medium-
OL,11,Fsized enterprises (SMEs) and start-ups
OL,12,Fin Northern Ireland by making it
OL,13,Feasier for them to enter the defence
OL,14,Fsupply chain.
OL,16,FIt will also focus on supporting SMEs
OL,17,Fin developing technology that can be
OL,18,Fused for military and civilian
OL,19,Fpurposes, ensuring new technologies
OL,20,Fbenefit UK national security and the
OL,21,Fwider economy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FAlongside the #50 million investment,
OL,8,Fthe UK Government has said it will
OL,9,Fprovide additional funding for a
OL,10,Fskills initiative in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FDUP Deputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,13,FPengelly attended the event.
OL,15,FSinn Fein's Vice President said she
OL,16,Fdoesn't agree with the Government's
OL,17,Fpolicy choice.
OL,26,@wD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
