OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,F"I'm very comfortable that, of course,
OL,8,Fany business here, whenever London
OL,9,Fmakes a policy choice, as they have
OL,10,Fdone, to invest #50m in the
OL,11,Fmilitarisation agenda for the
OL,12,Fcompanies here, they'll want to take
OL,13,Fadvantage of that, and I wouldn't
OL,14,Fblame them for that.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,F"We do want to grow our economy and
OL,8,Fcreate opportunities and we've seen
OL,9,Freally good advances right across our
OL,10,Feconomy, but where we do have a
OL,11,Fdifference with London and
OL,12,Fparticularly the British Government,
OL,13,Fis the fact that they are prioritizing
OL,14,Fweapons of war over people, and
OL,15,Fthey're prioritizing weapons of war
OL,16,Fover investment in health, education,
OL,17,Fchildcare, or any other public
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,F"So I don't agree with this as a
OL,8,Fpolicy choice. However, I do want to
OL,9,Fgrow our economy, so I think you can
OL,10,Fhold both of those positions at one
OL,11,Ftime. I don't agree with this decision
OL,12,Fbeing taken in London. This money
OL,13,Fcould be much better spent."
OL,15,FWhen asked about Stormont's financial
OL,16,Flandscape, Ms O'Neill branded a
OL,17,FTreasury analysis of Stormont's
OL,18,Ffinances as 'nonsense'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
