OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FThe Open Book Review of the Northern
OL,8,FIreland Executive Budget concluded
OL,9,Fthat Stormont ministers could make
OL,10,Fdecisions which would unlock up to
OL,11,F#3.3 billion in additional spending
OL,12,Fpower each year.
OL,14,FThe Review also said if powersharing
OL,15,Fministers had taken forward "even an
OL,16,Feighth" of options available to them,
OL,17,Fthey might have avoided a budget
OL,18,Foverspend in the last financial year.
OL,26,@wD@]OUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FMs O'Neill said: "I think it is
OL,8,Fnonsense, to be quite frank, I think
OL,9,Fit's lazy. We participated in that
OL,10,Fopen book review for a reason, because
OL,11,Fwe think we have a strong case to
OL,12,Fmake. When you look at how we're
OL,13,Ffunded in comparison to Scotland and
OL,14,FWales, there's a direct inequality. If
OL,15,Fwe were funded to the same tune above
OL,16,Fthe level of need that's been
OL,17,Fidentified in Wales, we would have an
OL,18,Fadditional 1.1bn. If we're funded in
OL,19,Fthe same tune as Scotland, we would
OL,20,Fhave an additional 3bn. All parties of
OL,21,Fthe Executive are united in this. It's
OL,22,Fimpossible to agree a budget based on
OL,23,Fwhat we have right now."
OL,26,@oD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
