FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FLast year, a High Court judgement
OL,8,Fquashed the Stormont Executive's move
OL,9,Fto approve the #1.2 billion A5 road
OL,10,Fscheme, after a legal challenge from a
OL,11,Fgroup including residents, farmers and
OL,12,Flandowners.
OL,14,FThe judge said the proposals breached
OL,15,Fsections of Northern Ireland's Climate
OL,16,FChange Act as they did not demonstrate
OL,17,Fhow they would comply with the
OL,18,Fcommitment to reach net-zero carbon
OL,19,Femissions by 2050.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FSinn Fein Infrastructure Minister Liz
OL,8,FKimmins is appealing the High Court
OL,9,Fjudgement.
OL,11,FFollowing a meeting between Minister
OL,12,FKimmins and the Ulster Farmers' Union
OL,13,F(UFU) on Monday, the UFU welcomed a
OL,14,Fcommitment from the Minister that
OL,15,Fconstruction on the A5 will not begin
OL,16,Fbefore 1 January 2027.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,FMs O'Neill said: "The A5 has been
OL,8,Fcaught up in a legal challenge,
OL,9,Funfortunately, and that is to the
OL,10,Fregret of everybody, because I think
OL,11,Fthe political will is there to build
OL,12,Fthat road, and it will be built, but
OL,13,Fwe need to work our way through the
OL,14,Flegal challenges.
OL,26,@oD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,F"The reality is that the court case is
OL,8,Fyet to be heard. It's going to be
OL,9,Fheard in June. We're expecting to get
OL,10,Fa judgment in September. So
OL,11,Frealistically, we can't get diggers on
OL,12,Fthe ground again until January, at the
OL,13,Fearliest. I'm hopeful that that will
OL,14,Fbe the case, because I think that
OL,15,Fcommon sense needs prevail in the
OL,16,Fcourt. We need to get this project
OL,17,Fbuilt. And I think the case that's
OL,18,Fbeen mounted against it actually
OL,19,Fshould successfully be defeated,
OL,20,Fbecause this is a road that's led to
OL,21,Fover 50 people losing their lives.
OL,22,FThis is a strategic project that we
OL,23,Fneed to see delivered.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777071785
OL,3,CFirst Minister 'very comfortable' with
OL,4,Cdefence growth deal announcement
OL,5,Cabsence
OL,7,F"There is still a lot more time in
OL,8,Fwhich to deliver, but I will stand
OL,9,Fvery firmly on our ministerial
OL,10,Fachievements to date, on what
OL,11,Fcollectively, we've been able to
OL,12,Fachieve as an Executive. I will not be
OL,13,Fcomplacent, because I do think it's
OL,14,Fimportant to say we've had two years
OL,15,Fwith another year to go. I think very
OL,16,Fmuch it's about laying foundations for
OL,17,Fwhat we can do in the next mandate."
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/18
